                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Why do so many enchanters complain about nerfs?  We are still one of the most powerful classes in the game even after the nerf.  We have no trouble getting groups except for pre-60 due to people getting KEI and even that is soon to be remedied by SoE.
<br />

<br />
What about keeping a 500 dps pet easily is reasonable to you?  When you made your enchanter were you thinking "I'm gonna do more damage than the rest of the group put together?"
<br />

<br />
I think it's wonderful to be able, with assistance, and for a short time, rescue a bad situation by charming a pet.  That we can charm such obscene pets for long periods of time is crazy.
<br />

<br />
Don't complain, you could be a rogue, monk, or necromancer.
<br />

<br />
Qest T. Silverclaw: Timetwister Extraordinaire
<br />
Guildleader of Zero Sum on the Mithaniel Marr server</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
