                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>sleepy wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Before creating my chanter I looked at all the classes spells and abilities to pick the class I wanted. The chanter's charm was very attractive to me and is a major reason I created him. </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
