You chose a class based on one spell?
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">So yes charm is a big disapointment, it's not like we never had it, we did, we became chanters because of it and they took it away. </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
