Took it away? I still use it all the time. I personally picked an Enchanter for other reasons. I didn't discover the fun of charming til about level 25. You said you picked an Enchanter because you liked charm. It sounds like you picked Enchanter because you wanted the easiest and fastest xp possible. Your xp may have slowed down a bit, but I think you will find your charm spells are still in your little spellbook. If you truly started your Enchanter because of their charm ability, this wouldn't bother you. Did you know the xp %'s before you started and based your choice off of that?
